subject: Football (College)
Rose Bowl (Football Game)
Heisman Trophy
lead_paragraph: Florida State, an underdog by more than a touchdown, will play the lack-of-respect card against Oregon in a game that features this season’s and last season’s Heisman Trophy winners.
